    "faq": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_1": { "type": "faq_item", "settings": { "question": "What causes vaginal dryness?", "answer": "<p>Vaginal dryness is typically caused by an imbalance of hormones, which is most commonly experienced during menopause, perimenopause, and breastfeeding. During these pivotal life phases, estrogen levels drastically drop or fluctuate, causing our vaginal tissue to lose its natural moisture and strength, resulting in vaginal dryness. On the other hand, vaginal dryness can also be a symptom of bacterial vaginosis (BV), yeast infection, or a general imbalance in the microflora.</p>" } },
        "faq_2": { "type": "faq_item", "settings": { "question": "What types of issues does Vaginal Moisturizer help with?", "answer": "<p>Vaginal Moisturizer can provide immediate relief and long-term lubricating support for anyone experiencing pain or discomfort associated with vaginal dryness. Symptoms of vaginal dryness include itching, burning, soreness, pain during intercourse, and abnormal discharge. Our formula may also alleviate general discomfort associated with microflora imbalances.</p>" } },
        "faq_3": { "type": "faq_item", "settings": { "question": "Is hyaluronic acid safe for internal use?", "answer": "<p>Not only is it 100% safe, but it\u2019s also incredibly beneficial for restoring your vulvovaginal moisture. Hyaluronic acid is a substance that naturally occurs in your body and is particularly abundant in your skin, eyes, and connective tissues. Imagine a gooey or gel-like molecule that helps keep things lubricated and moisturized.</p>" } },
        "faq_4": { "type": "faq_item", "settings": { "question": "Why suppositories?", "answer": "<p>Vaginal suppositories provide efficient nutrient delivery by bypassing the digestive system, allowing direct absorption in the targeted area. This method often results in faster and more effective nutrient uptake compared to oral alternatives. It\u2019s like taking a shortcut to deliver the goods exactly where they\u2019re needed, optimizing the benefits of the nutrients.</p>" } },
        "faq_5": { "type": "faq_item", "settings": { "question": "How long before I see results?", "answer": "<p>Our clinical trials showed that our vaginal moisturizer with hyaluronic acid produced visible results in just one day! However, remember that everybody is unique\u2014including our metabolic systems and microbiomes\u2014meaning that results may vary.</p>" } },
        "faq_6": { "type": "faq_item", "settings": { "question": "Does Vaginal Moisturizer have any side effects?", "answer": "<p>Our clinical studies showed no serious adverse side effects. All Neycher\u2019s products are scientifically formulated with all-natural, plant-based, and organic ingredients, which makes them microbiome and pH-friendly. However, please review our ingredient list to avoid adverse reactions due to allergies and personal sensitivity.</p>" } }
      },
      "block_order": ["faq_1", "faq_2", "faq_3", "faq_4", "faq_5", "faq_6"],
